metadata.name: Cyber Cologne
metadata.description:
Edition title: Cyber Cologne

The city lights pulse, the town is alive.  
The train picks up, those that don't drive.  
From A to B we reach our destination,  
and when the train is on time, it deserves a standing ovation.

DracheTech11
